Add `claudeEventUnsub` to the cleanup in `onCleanup`.

### Step 4: Tests

**`gui/src/__tests__/claudeBridge.test.ts`** — unit tests for bridge wrappers:
- Mock `@tauri-apps/api/core` invoke and `@tauri-apps/api/event` listen
